content:
Please find the restaurants that appear in Day 1 of the Travel Itinerary database, then create corresponding entries in the Expenses database, one restaurant per entry. Set the date uniformly to Jan 1, 2025, and the cost uniformly to $120. Display the restaurant name in the Expense field. Set Category to Dining. For Comment, use the Description from the corresponding restaurant page. Leave other properties empty.

Note: Based on your understanding, solve the task all at once by yourself, don't ask for my opinions on anything.

content.text:
Excellent! I found 5 restaurants from Day 1:
1. Rikuro's Namba Main Branch - "Fluffy pancakes\n9AM-8PM"
2. Masahiko Ozumi Paris - "10 AM–7 PM, Close on Weds \n950 yen Crochet donuts"
3. Riceball Gori-chan Namba - "11 AM–8 PM, closed on Tuesdays\n350 yen, cash only"
4. Takoume Honten (Oden) - "Oden"
5. Unagi Kushiyaki Idumo - "Unadon (grilled eel rice bowl)\n11 AM–10 PM"
